### 方案1：纯Java2D字幕渲染（推荐 - 最稳定）- 正确token
POST http://localhost:8081/api/subtitles/burn-local-srt
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: sf_token_2024_admin

{
  "videoPath": "C:\\Users\\NVIDIA\\Desktop\\a.mp4",
  "subtitlePath": "C:\\Users\\NVIDIA\\Desktop\\aaa.srt"
}

### 方案1：纯Java2D字幕渲染 - Bearer token格式
POST http://localhost:8081/api/subtitles/burn-local-srt
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer sf_token_2024_user1

{
  "videoPath": "C:\\Users\\NVIDIA\\Desktop\\a.mp4",
  "subtitlePath": "C:\\Users\\NVIDIA\\Desktop\\aaa.srt"
}

